description: The demolition of existing buildings at St Clements Heights, 165 Wells Park Road SE26 and the construction of 7 four to six storey buildings, comprising 50 one and two bedroom Almshouses and 46 two, three and four bedroom self-contained flats and houses, together with the provision of 76 car parking spaces, vehicular accesses onto Sydenham Hill and Wells Park Road with associated landscaping. (Outline Application).
